parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PTU can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver. It can also cause the vehicle to shut off without warning, resulting in a loss of control.
symptoms: The "Service 4WD" or "Service Shifter" warning message appears on the dashboard
the vehicle loses power or stalls
the vehicle shuts off without warning
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle vibrates or makes abnormal noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter gear harness or PTU can cause the vehicle to lose power or shut off without warning, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The "Service Shifter" warning message appears on the dashboard
the shifter gear harness fails
the PTU fails
the vehicle loses power or stalls
the transmission slips or hesitates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power or shut off without warning, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle loses power or stalls
the vehicle shuts off without warning
the "Service 4WD" or "Service Shifter" warning message appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the service shifter can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The service shifter light comes on
all gear lights on the shifter panel light up in red
the vehicle slows down or stalls
the engine feels like it's slipping
the gas pedal is unresponsive
and the airbag and parking brake notifications flash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic parking brake can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to potential accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The parking brake engages randomly
the vehicle will not move forward or backward
and the parking brake warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle slows down or stalls
and the service transmission warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The water leak can cause electrical issues, leading to potential fires or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: Water leaks into the vehicle
causing electrical issues
burning smells
and potential fires.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Vehicle Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the vehicle can cause loss of power, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the engine shuts off
and the vehicle will not restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The service shifter error can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety concerns, such as loss of control or accidents, especially if the issue occurs while driving.
symptoms: The "Service Shifter" message appears on the dashboard
all lights on the shifter turn red
the vehicle may shift into neutral or park unexpectedly
and the parking brake may engage without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PTU can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The "Service 4WD" message appears on the dashboard
the vehicle may experience loss of traction or stability
and the PTU may need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic park brake can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The parking brake engages without warning
the vehicle may roll or move unexpectedly
and the parking brake may need to be repaired or replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The separation of the front leather dash can cause a distraction to the driver, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The front leather dash becomes separated
potentially obstructing the driver's view.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause accidents or injuries, especially if the vehicle is traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates rapidly without warning
potentially leading to loss of control or accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety concerns, such as loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle may shift into neutral or park unexpectedly
the transmission may slip or hesitate
and the vehicle may experience difficulty shifting gears.
